      "review_summary": "The branch adds `includeFamily`/`resetAncestors` history controls, a shared reset-family transcript target resolver, and a prompt transform that prepends one reset-ancestor compaction summary to embedded-agent context.\n\nPR surface: Source +352, Tests +541, Other +4. Total +897 across 40 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-level: current main and v2026.6.6 have no family selector or automatic carryover path, and the PR's embedded-tool parity gap is visible from `createOpenClawTools` wiring embedded runs to a stub that ignores `includeFamily`. I did not run a live reset-channel scenario in this read-only review.",
